The Lout mailing list

A public mailing list has been set up for discussion
of the Lout document formatting system.  Thanks to
Rodrigo Vanegas of Brown University for starting this
list, to former maintainers Valeriy E. Ushakov and
Greg Woods, and to the current initiator, Ludovic
Courtes.

To subscribe to the list or unsubscribe, visit

    http://lists.nongnu.org/mailman/listinfo/lout-users

To post a message (only subscribers can do this), send email to

    lout-users@nongnu.org

It will be forwarded by email to all current subscribers.
